azyYiu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2FCrazyYiu&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvt7g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=c2a3a536\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/CrazyYiu</a>"},{"pid":"4ce8d63d20ea81dc85fea8954377be6867c827ff","tid":2488315,"uid":22695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:27:48.000Z","msg":"以下係呢個POST既目錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>1. 咩叫CAGED System</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>1.1 </ins>Maj Scale的五大位置<br />\n  <br />\n<ins>1.2</ins> 不同Barre Chord形態<br />\n<br />\n<ins>1.3</ins> Minor角度看CAGED System<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>2. 如何應用CAGED System</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>2.1</ins> 上/下行Scale 記憶大法<br />\n<br />\n<ins>2.2</ins> Chord tone solo<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>3. Blues(藍調)</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>3.1</ins>藍調音樂背景<br />\n<br />\n<ins>3.2 </ins>必聽人物介紹<br />\n<br />\n<ins>3.3</ins> 基本節奏及Chord Progression<br />\n<br />\n<ins>3.4 </ins>Blues Scale<br />\n<br />\n<ins>3.5</ins> Maj，Min及Blues Scale混合應用"},{"pid":"f6e9f43eb71e9b7cde1316b8b1126c5052975a66","tid":2488315,"uid":22695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:31:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">學習CAGED system目的</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我細個學結他一開始係學chord再配合下唔同既節奏彈下歌仔<br />\n<br />\n但有一日我聽到呢首歌覺得好神奇 佢係做緊chord定solo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果一刻我覺得自己係零<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明我背熟哂唔同scale pattern 點解我完全唔明佢做緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lZ4pK4ElnAM&amp;ab_channel=KiryuKazumaRadioPlaylist\" data-sr-url=\"ht